      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation software (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2) under documented version control with regression test suite passing at release; FDA-validated solver benchmarks on file.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used throughout. Version control via Git with tagged release. Regression test suite of 47 benchmark cases executed; all pass. FDA solver benchmark documentation on file. Required and achieved levels both Gradation 2."
