      "rationale": "Euler-Bernoulli beam bending analytical solution comparison yields 0.3% error. Hertzian contact patch size comparison yields 0.7% error. Both within 1% criterion. Code verification complete."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
