      "rationale": "Validation uses the identical non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw geometry and Ti-6Al-4V material as the COU. ASTM F1717 loading is the regulatory standard for the intended submission. Both laboratories are ISO 17025 accredited. Validation activity is directly relevant to the COU with no significant extrapolation required."
    }
